  "akureyri.D.list.1.bio": "Berglind Ósk Guðmundsdóttir is a lawyer, born on 7 July 1993, and a former member of Alþingi for the North East constituency from 2021 to 2024 for the Independence Party. She completed BA and ML degrees in law at the University of Akureyri and earned a doctorate in 2021. She is the lead candidate for the Independence Party in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections.",
