  "akureyri.D.list.2.bio": "Heimir Örn Árnason is chair of the town council in Akureyri and a department head at Naustaskóli, where he has taught and worked in school management for more than 16 years. He is placed second on the Independence Party list in Akureyri.",
  "akureyri.D.list.2.occupation": "Town councillor",
