  "akureyri.L.list.1.bio": "Óðinn Svan Óðinsson is a media professional and former journalist and programme director at RÚV, where he worked for around seven years from 2019 as the North Iceland correspondent and later in sports programming. He holds a degree in media studies from the University of Akureyri and was born and raised in Akureyri. He left his position at RÚV in February 2026 to focus on politics and leads the L-list.",
