  "akureyri.L.list.2.bio": "Brynja Hlíf Þorsteinsdóttir is a biomedical scientist and current VG town councillor in Akureyri, and is placed second on the L-list in the 2026 municipal elections. She has previously held positions of trust for the party at local government level.",
