  "akureyri.L.list.3.bio": "Preben Jón Pétursson is a dairy technologist and is placed third on the L-list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections. He is part of a diverse L-list made up of people from different backgrounds with shared goals for Akureyri.",
  "akureyri.L.list.3.occupation": "Dairy technologist",
  "akureyri.L.list.4.bio": "María Pálsdóttir is an actress and entrepreneur and is placed fourth on the L-list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections. She brings together the arts and entrepreneurship with participation in local government affairs.",
  "akureyri.L.list.4.occupation": "Actress and entrepreneur",
  "akureyri.L.list.5.bio": "Andri Teitsson is an engineer and current VG town councillor in Akureyri, and is placed fifth on the L-list in the 2026 municipal elections. As a town councillor, he has been involved in decisions on the building up and development of Akureyri.",
