  "akureyri.M.list.4.bio": "Katrín Vilhjálmsdóttir is a beautician and healthcare assistant and is in 4th place on the Miðflokkurinn list in Akureyri for the 2026 municipal elections. She combines expertise in the healthcare and service sectors.",
  "akureyri.M.list.4.occupation": "Beautician and healthcare assistant",
  "akureyri.M.list.5.bio": "Hannes Karlsson is a managing director and is in 5th place on the Miðflokkurinn list in Akureyri. He has been active in Miðflokkur Akureyrar, including as the party's managing director. He lives in Lerkilundur in Akureyri.",
