  "akureyri.S.list.2.bio": "Hanna Dóra Markúsdóttir is a primary school teacher and is placed second on the Social Democratic Alliance list in Akureyri for the 2026 municipal elections. She supports the party’s vision of a stronger school town and a better education system.",
