  "akureyri.V.agenda.2.title": "Housing",
  "akureyri.V.list.1.bio": "Jana Salóme Ingibjargar Jósepsdóttir is a chemist by training, with a degree from the University of Iceland (2015), and has also completed studies in human resource management. She is a town councillor in Akureyri, born on 8 January 1991, and has served as national secretary of Vinstri græn and sat on Akureyri Town's environment and transport committee. She leads the VG list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections.",
