  "akureyri.V.list.3.bio": "Ásrún Ýr Gestsdóttir is an entrepreneur originally from Hrísey and is in 3rd place on the VG list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections. She has previously been on the VG candidate list in Akureyri.",
  "akureyri.V.list.3.occupation": "Entrepreneur",
  "akureyri.V.list.4.bio": "Sigtryggur Ellertsson is an eco-friendly shop owner and is in 4th place on the VG list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections. He has written about the development of central Akureyri and places emphasis on environmental issues in his business operations.",
  "akureyri.V.list.4.occupation": "Businessman",
  "akureyri.V.list.5.bio": "Herdís Júlía Júlíusdóttir is training to become an occupational therapist and is in 5th place on the VG list in Akureyri in the 2026 municipal elections. She has been on the VG candidate list in Akureyri in previous elections and is part of a new generation of left-wingers in North Iceland.",
