  "arborg.B.list.3.bio": "Arnar Freyr Ólafsson is an international finance specialist from Eyrarbakki and heads Framsókn's list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections as lead candidate. He emphasises financial sustainability and the development of the municipality in Suðurland.",
  "arborg.B.list.3.occupation": "Municipal councillor, managing director",
  "arborg.B.list.4.bio": "Guðrún Rakel Svandísardóttir is a headteacher and trained environmental planner and is on Framsókn's list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections. She combines experience from school leadership and environmental issues in her election campaign.",
  "arborg.B.list.4.occupation": "Headteacher",
  "arborg.B.list.5.bio": "Magnús Benediktsson is an operations manager and is in 5th place on Framsókn's list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections. He brings operational experience to the candidate list, which seeks to strengthen Árborg's development.",
  "arborg.B.list.5.occupation": "Operations manager",
