  "arborg.C.list.19.occupation": "Student",
  "arborg.C.list.2.bio": "Guðný Björk Pálmadóttir is a designer and innovation engineer and is in 2nd place on the Viðreisn list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections. This is the first time that Viðreisn is standing in local council elections in Árborg.",
