  "arborg.D.list.19.occupation": "Managing director",
  "arborg.D.list.2.bio": "Sveinn Ægir Birgisson is Chair of the Town Council in Árborg, a 28-year-old from Selfoss, and is in 2nd place on the Independence Party’s list in Árborg. He has served the municipality’s residents as a town councillor and committee chair for four years, and was previously active in the youth council.",
