  "arborg.S.list.1.bio": "Sigurjón Vídalín Guðmundsson is a geologist and surveyor, born in Eyrarbakki. He runs his own geotechnical and consultancy company, Geotækni ehf., and also works as a specialist at the Icelandic Road and Coastal Administration in the southern region. He founded the movements Áfram Árborg (2018) and later joined Viðreisn and finally the Social Democratic Alliance. He is chair of Árborg’s town council and leads the Social Democratic Alliance’s S-list in the 2026 municipal elections.",
