  "arborg.S.list.2.bio": "Margrét Björk Ólafsdóttir is a director of nursing and is in 2nd place on the Social Democratic Alliance and independents list in Árborg for the 2026 municipal elections. She brings extensive experience in healthcare management to the candidate list.",
