  "arborg.S.list.22.occupation": "Project manager and town councillor",
  "arborg.S.list.3.bio": "Brynjar Þór Elvarsson is a public administration specialist and is in 3rd place on the Social Democratic Alliance and independents list in Árborg for the 2026 municipal elections. He brings knowledge of administration and public affairs to the candidate list.",
  "arborg.S.list.3.occupation": "Public administration specialist",
  "arborg.S.list.4.bio": "Elísabet Björgvinsdóttir is an entertainment manager, social media manager and coach, and is in 4th place on the Social Democratic Alliance and Independents list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections. She brings together experience from cultural work, social media and coaching in her candidacy.",
  "arborg.S.list.4.occupation": "Entertainment manager and coach",
  "arborg.S.list.5.bio": "Árni Magnússon is a project manager and is in 5th place on the Social Democratic Alliance and Independents list in Árborg in the 2026 municipal elections. He brings project management experience to a diverse and experienced candidate list.",
