  "borgarbyggd.B.list.1.bio": "Davíð Sigurðsson is Chair of the Borgarbyggð municipal council executive committee and a farmer. He has served as a managing director and municipal councillor in Borgarbyggð and was placed second on the Progressive Party list in the 2022 elections. Only one candidacy was submitted in the party’s leadership selection ahead of the 2026 elections — Davíð’s own — and it was approved at a meeting of the Progressive Association of Borgarfjörður and Mýrasýsla. He is experienced in municipal affairs and well known to residents of the area.",
