  "fjallabyggd.D.list.1.bio": "Tómas Atli Einarsson is 50 years old, born in Reykjavík but moved to Ólafsfjörður in 1995. He is the managing director and owner of Skiltagerð Norðurlands, a snow observer for the Icelandic Meteorological Office, chairman of the Tindur rescue team, and harbour master in Fjallabyggð. He is married, has three children and four grandchildren, and has served on the Fjallabyggð municipal council for four years.",
