  "fjallabyggd.H.list.1.bio": "Helgi Jóhannsson leads the H-list of Bæjarmálafélagið in Fjallabyggð, known as “For the Whole,” in the 2026 municipal elections. He is a financial adviser and service manager at Arion banki in Ólafsfjörður and has lived in the fjords for almost all his life. Among other things, he has been involved in the development of restaurants and guesthouses and in the restoration of an old wooden ship, Freymundur ÓF.",
