  "fjardabyggd.B.list.2.bio": "Birgir Jónsson is an upper secondary school teacher and has served on the Fjarðabyggð town council. He is in second place on the Progressive Party's B-list in Fjarðabyggð for 2026 and has expertise in the school system.",
