  "fjardabyggd.B.list.3.bio": "Helga Rakel Arnardóttir is an office manager and paramedic who is in third place on the Progressive Party's B-list in Fjarðabyggð for the 2026 local elections. She combines management experience with healthcare expertise.",
  "fjardabyggd.B.list.3.occupation": "Office manager and paramedic",
  "fjardabyggd.B.list.4.bio": "Sigurjón Andrés Jónasson is in fourth place on the Progressive Party's B-list in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 local elections. The list emphasises the municipality's development and progress in rural Iceland.",
