  "fjardabyggd.B.list.5.bio": "Bjarney Birta Bergsdóttir is in 5th place on Framsókn’s B-list in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 municipal elections. Framsókn in Fjarðabyggð presented the list at a meeting in Þórðarbúð in Reyðarfjörður.",
