  "fjardabyggd.D.list.1.bio": "Ragnar Sigurðsson is the managing director of the nursing homes in Fjarðabyggð and Chair of Fjarðabyggð’s town executive council. He completed a BA degree in law from Háskólinn á Akureyri and an MLM degree from Háskólinn á Bifröst, and pursued MBA studies at the University of the Highlands and Islands. Ragnar lives in Reyðarfjörður and has taken an active part in the Independence Party since his youth. He has been the lead candidate of the Independence Party in Fjarðabyggð since 2022 and was reselected unopposed for the same role for the 2026 elections.",
