  "fjardabyggd.D.list.2.bio": "Kristinn Þór Jónasson is a service manager and Independence Party town councillor in Fjarðabyggð, placed 2nd on the D-list for 2026. He has served on Fjarðabyggð town council during the current term.",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.2.occupation": "Service manager",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.3.bio": "Þórdís Mjöll Benediktsdóttir is the headteacher of Dalborg preschool in Eskifjörður and an Independence Party town councillor in Fjarðabyggð, placed 3rd on the D-list for 2026. She is the mother of two children and has devoted herself to education and upbringing.",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.3.occupation": "Preschool headteacher",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.4.bio": "Húnbogi Sólon Gunnþórsson is a project manager, placed 4th on the Independence Party’s D-list in Fjarðabyggð for 2026. He works for SVN and brings experience in project management.",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.4.occupation": "Project manager",
  "fjardabyggd.D.list.5.bio": "Tanja Tómasdóttir is an assistant to the quality manager, placed 5th on the Independence Party’s D-list in Fjarðabyggð for 2026. She brings knowledge of quality management to the municipal council.",
