  "fjardabyggd.M.list.2.bio": "Alma Sigurbjörnsdóttir is chief psychologist at Fjarðabyggð and is in 2nd place on the Centre Party’s M-list in the 2026 municipal elections. She brings specialist expertise in psychological services and welfare affairs.",
