  "fjardabyggd.M.list.3.bio": "Baldur Marteinn Einarsson is operations manager at Eskja and a member of Hið Íslenska Sjávarútvegsfræðafélag, and is in 3rd place on the Centre Party’s M-list in Fjarðabyggð in 2026. He brings specialist expertise in fisheries and operations.",
  "fjardabyggd.M.list.3.occupation": "Transport manager",
  "fjardabyggd.M.list.4.bio": "Hafþór Eiríksson is in 4th place on the Centre Party’s M-list in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 municipal elections. The Centre Party in Fjarðabyggð submitted its candidate list in March 2026.",
  "fjardabyggd.M.list.4.occupation": "Operations manager",
  "fjardabyggd.M.list.5.bio": "Anna Guðný Gunnarsdóttir is in 5th place on the Centre Party’s M-list in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 municipal elections. The list emphasises diverse professional expertise for the benefit of the municipality.",
