  "fjardabyggd.S.list.1.bio": "Stefán Þór Eysteinsson was born and raised in Neskaupstaður and works as a specialist and Head of Department at Matís ohf. in Neskaupstaður. He holds a BA in Biology from Gonzaga University in the United States, a master's degree in food science and a doctorate from the University of Iceland. Stefán has been active in the municipal affairs of Fjarðabyggð and leads the list of the Social Democratic Alliance and social democrats in the 2026 elections. He places emphasis on equality between settlements, consultation with residents and the development of basic services.",
