  "fjardabyggd.S.list.2.bio": "Hjördís Helga Seljan is an education consultant and municipal councillor for Fjarðalistinn from Reyðarfjörður who leads the S-list in Fjarðabyggð in 2026. She has served on the municipal council since 2018 and served as president of the council.",
