  "fjardabyggd.S.list.3.bio": "Valborg Ösp Á. Warén is a project manager in 3rd place on the S-list of Fjarðalistinn in Fjarðabyggð in 2026. She brings experience in project management and organisation.",
  "fjardabyggd.S.list.3.occupation": "Project manager",
  "fjardabyggd.S.list.4.bio": "Adam Ingi Guðlaugsson is in 4th place on the S-list of Fjarðalistinn in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 municipal elections. The list consists of members of Fjarðalistinn and the Social Democratic Alliance who have worked together on the municipal council.",
  "fjardabyggd.S.list.4.occupation": "Engineer and electrician",
  "fjardabyggd.S.list.5.bio": "Arndís Bára Pétursdóttir is in 5th place on the S-list of Fjarðalistinn in Fjarðabyggð in the 2026 municipal elections. Fjarðalistinn has fielded a list in municipal elections since 1998.",
