  "gardabaer.B.list.1.bio": "Hlynur Elías Bæringsson is the Deputy Mayor of Garðabær and Operations Manager of Stjarnan’s basketball division. He is known as one of Iceland’s greatest basketball players of all time and won the Icelandic championship title twice, most recently with Stjarnan in 2025 when he retired from playing. He was born on 6 July 1982 and leads Framsókn’s B-list in Garðabær.",
