  "gardabaer.B.list.2.bio": "Anna Margrét Steingrímsdóttir is a Marketing and Service Manager with a master’s degree in service studies and a BSc in marketing and international business from the University of Iceland. She is in 2nd place on Framsókn’s B-list in Garðabær in the 2026 municipal elections.",
