  "gardabaer.B.list.22.occupation": "Managing Director",
  "gardabaer.B.list.3.bio": "Einar Þór Einarsson is a Managing Director and is in 3rd place on Framsókn’s B-list in Garðabær in the 2026 municipal elections.",
  "gardabaer.B.list.3.occupation": "Managing Director",
  "gardabaer.B.list.4.bio": "Einar Bárðarson is a self-employed consultant and Managing Director and is in 4th place on Framsókn’s B-list in Garðabær. He was in second place on Framsókn’s list in Reykjavík in the 2024 parliamentary elections.",
  "gardabaer.B.list.4.occupation": "Managing Director",
  "gardabaer.B.list.5.bio": "Inga Amal Hasan is a lawyer and is in 5th place on Framsókn’s B-list in Garðabær in the 2026 municipal elections.",
