  "gardabaer.C.list.1.bio": "Guðlaugur Kristmundsson is the former executive director of the Viðreisn parliamentary group (2020–2021) and has held a variety of roles, including serving as Managing Director of FlyOver Iceland since 2023. He was a deputy town councillor for Viðreisn in Garðabær during the last electoral term and now leads Viðreisn’s C-list in the 2026 municipal elections.",
