  "gardabaer.C.list.2.bio": "Harpa Þorsteinsdóttir is a public health specialist and has served as a deputy town councillor for Viðreisn in Garðabær. She is ranked second on Viðreisn’s C-list and has taken part in town council meetings on welfare issues and health promotion.",
