  "gardabaer.C.list.22.occupation": "Former town councillor",
  "gardabaer.C.list.3.bio": "Jón Bjarni Steinsson is a lawyer and event organiser, including as owner of the restaurants Dillon and Pablo Discobar in Reykjavík. He is ranked third on Viðreisn’s C-list in Garðabær and has written about the town’s development in 2026.",
  "gardabaer.C.list.3.occupation": "Candidate",
  "gardabaer.C.list.4.bio": "Sigríður Þóra Ásgeirsdóttir is a filmmaker and entrepreneur, founder of Úlfatími. She worked as production manager on Áramótaskaupið at RÚV and is ranked fourth on Viðreisn’s C-list in Garðabær.",
  "gardabaer.C.list.4.occupation": "Candidate",
  "gardabaer.C.list.5.bio": "Hreiðar Þór Jónsson is a managing director and consultant, and former CEO of the digital publishing company Datera. He is ranked fifth on Viðreisn’s C-list in Garðabær and has a background in sales and marketing at Ölgerðin and international companies.",
  "gardabaer.C.list.5.occupation": "Candidate",
