  "gardabaer.D.list.1.bio": "Almar Guðmundsson is the Mayor of Garðabær and took office in June 2022 following the municipal elections. He is an economist with an MBA from London Business School and has worked in finance and business, including as Managing Director of the Federation of Icelandic Industries from 2009 to 2017. Almar was born on 3 May 1972, has roots in Garðabær, and is married to Guðrún Zoega.",
  "gardabaer.D.list.1.interests.0": "Responsible financial management and debt reduction",
