  "gardabaer.GB.list.2.bio": "Guðjón Pétur Lýðsson is an entrepreneur and former professional footballer who played, among other clubs, for Helsingborg in Sweden and won the Roman league championship. He has built up a real estate empire and is in 2nd place on Garðabæjarlistinn's GB list in the 2026 municipal elections.",
