  "gardabaer.GB.list.3.bio": "Joanna Marcinkowska is a project manager who has worked on integration and multicultural affairs in Iceland. She is in 3rd place on Garðabæjarlistinn's GB list in the 2026 municipal elections.",
  "gardabaer.GB.list.3.occupation": "Inclusion project manager",
  "gardabaer.GB.list.4.bio": "Finnur Jónsson is a leisure counsellor and teacher and is in 4th place on Garðabæjarlistinn's GB list in the 2026 municipal elections.",
  "gardabaer.GB.list.4.occupation": "Homeroom teacher",
  "gardabaer.GB.list.5.bio": "Baldur Ó. Svavarsson is an architect (FAÍ and FSSA) and co-owner of Úti og inni arkitektar, a consultancy firm founded in 1989. He is in 5th place on Garðabæjarlistinn's GB list.",
