  "gardabaer.M.list.3.bio": "Snorri Marteinsson is a chief financial officer and works as an executive at Wells Fargo Securities. He is in 3rd place on the Centre Party’s M-list in Garðabær and was also in 3rd place on the party’s list in 2022.",
