  "hafnarfjordur.A.agenda.5.title": "A safe community",
  "hafnarfjordur.A.list.1.bio": "Ester Bíbí Ásgeirsdóttir is a project manager with a master’s degree in management and strategy. She has worked at the Icelandic Film Archive as head of legal deposit and promotional activities, and is also a musician. She leads the Left’s list in Hafnarfjörður in the 2026 municipal elections.",
  "hafnarfjordur.A.list.1.interests.0": "Housing",
