  "hornafjordur.B.list.1.bio": "Hjalti Þór Vignisson was born on 24 January 1978 in Hornafjörður and is Managing Director at Stormar — The Wild Taste of Iceland, a fish sales company specialising in the export of wild whitefish from Hornafjörður. He completed his matriculation examination at Fjölbrautaskólinn við Ármúla and earned a degree in political science from Háskóli Íslands. He previously served as municipal manager of Sveitarfélagið Hornafjörður and is Chair of the Board of Vatnajökulsþjóðgarður, appointed by the Minister for the Environment.",
