  "hunabyggd.B.list.1.bio": "Grímur Rúnar Lárusson is a lawyer in Blönduós and leads the B-list of the Progressive Party and progressives in Húnabyggð in the 2026 elections. He serves as vice-president of the Húnabyggð municipal council and is chair of the sports, leisure and public health committee. He describes his 18-person list as a blend of experience, ambition and commitment to the community.",
