  "hunabyggd.D.list.1.bio": "Guðmundur Haukur Jakobsson is a master plumber and managing director and has been president of the Húnabyggð municipal council since the municipality was established in 2022. Previously, he was president of the Blönduósbær municipal council. His D-list received 37.7% of the vote and 4 of 9 seats in 2022. He is once again leading the Independence Party members and independents in 2026 and describes the list as “capable people from towns and rural areas, of all ages, with diverse backgrounds.”",
