  "hunabyggd.HBA.list.1.bio": "Jón Gíslason is a farmer at Stóra-Búrfell and leads the All Together list in Húnabyggð in the 2026 elections. He has been the leader of Húnavatnshreppur since 2018 and headed the joint committee that examined the merger in Austur-Húnavatnssýsla, which led to the establishment of Húnabyggð in 2022. The All Together list brings together former members of the G and H lists from the 2022 elections.",
