  "isafjordur.S.agenda.2.title": "Education",
  "isafjordur.S.list.1.bio": "Svanfríður Guðrún Bergvinsdóttir is a business student and Chair of ASÍ-UNG and leads the S-list (The Social Democratic Alliance) in Ísafjarðarbær in the 2026 municipal elections; this is the first time in 24 years that the Social Democratic Alliance is contesting under its own banner in the municipality.",
