  "mulathing.M.list.1.bio": "Lárus Bjarnason is a lawyer and served as district commissioner in Austurland for more than thirty years — first in Norður-Múlasýsla from 1989, then as district commissioner in Austurland from 2015 until he left office in autumn 2024 upon reaching the age limit. He is a person with extensive knowledge of law and administration in Austurland. Lárus leads the Centre Party's candidate list in Múlaþing in the 2026 elections.",
