  "mulathing.V.agenda.0.text": "Protect the nature of Austurland and establish clear rules for environmentally sustainable development.",
  "mulathing.V.agenda.0.title": "Nature conservation",
  "mulathing.V.agenda.1.text": "Support a diverse economy — not only heavy industry but also knowledge-based industries, tourism and the creative sectors.",
