  "mulathing.V.list.1.bio": "Ásrún Mjöll Stefánsdóttir is a carpenter from Seyðisfjörður and has served on the Múlaþing municipal council for VG. She has campaigned for environmental issues in Austurland; among other things, she proposed installing monitoring equipment to measure air pollution in Múlaþing’s harbours caused by cruise ships in Seyðisfjörður. She leads the joint list of VG and independents in Múlaþing in the 2026 elections.",
