  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.1.bio": "Arnar Páll Guðmundsson is a business graduate and human resources consultant. He served as chair of Viðreisn in Suðurnes and leads the first Viðreisn list ever to stand in Reykjanesbær in the 2026 municipal elections. He has written articles on the economy and electoral issues for Vísir.",
