  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.2.bio": "Davíð Skarphéðinsson is a building technologist at the engineering consultancy Verkís and works in Suðurnes. He is second on Viðreisn’s candidate list in Reykjanesbær for the 2026 municipal elections.",
