  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.3.bio": "Ásta Kristín Guðmundsdóttir is a teacher and project manager at Reykjanesbær, where she has specialised in coordination and services for refugees and asylum seekers. She is third on Viðreisn’s candidate list in Reykjanesbær in 2026.",
  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.3.occupation": "Teacher and project manager",
  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.4.bio": "Aðalheiður Júlírós Óskarsdóttir is a quality manager and was elected chair of the Viðreisn association in Suðurnes at its founding meeting. She is fourth on Viðreisn’s candidate list in Reykjanesbær in 2026.",
  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.4.occupation": "Quality manager",
  "reykjanesbaer.C.list.5.bio": "Sveinn Enok Jóhannsson is a farmer in Höfn on Reykjanes. He is fifth on Viðreisn’s candidate list in Reykjanesbær in 2026 and took a seat on the board of the Viðreisn association in Suðurnes.",
