  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.2.bio": "Margrét Þórarinsdóttir is a senior flight attendant and a town councillor on Reykjanesbær Town Council. She led the Umbót list in the 2022 municipal elections and previously served on the council for the Centre Party from 2018 to 2022; in February 2026, Umbót merged with the Independence Party, and she is placed second on the party’s list.",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.2.occupation": "Senior flight attendant and town councillor",
