  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.21.occupation": "Managing Director of Nesraf",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.22.occupation": "Town councillor and outgoing lead candidate",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.3.bio": "Kristján Pétur Kristjánsson is the Managing Director of Konvin hotel by Keflavík Airport in Reykjanesbær. He is in third place on the Independence Party’s candidate list in Reykjanesbær for 2026.",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.3.occupation": "Managing Director of Konvin",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.4.bio": "Alexander Ragnarsson is a master carpenter and property manager at Aðaltorg in Reykjanesbær. He is a town councillor for the Independence Party and is in fourth place on the party’s candidate list for 2026.",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.4.occupation": "Master carpenter and town councillor",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.5.bio": "Guðbergur Reynisson is the Managing Director of Cargoflutningar ehf., a transport company between Reykjavík and Suðurnes that he founded in 2009. He is a town councillor for the Independence Party in Reykjanesbær and has been chairman of the Independence Party association in Reykjanesbær since 2016.",
  "reykjanesbaer.D.list.5.occupation": "Managing Director and town councillor",
