  "reykjavik.A.list.2.bio": "Líf Magneudóttir was born on 13 August 1974 in Copenhagen and moved to Iceland in 1975. She graduated with a teaching qualification from the Iceland University of Education in 2004. Líf has served on Reykjavík City Council since 2016 and became President of the City Executive Council on 21 February 2025.",
