  "reykjavik.A.list.3.bio": "Stefán Pálsson is a historian, born on 8 April 1975. He has worked as a translator, writer and participant in public debate, and is a former chair of the Icelandic Anti-War Association. He has published numerous books on Icelandic football and history, and leads walking tours through Reykjavík’s historic neighbourhoods.",
