  "reykjavik.A.list.4.bio": "Ásta Þórdís Skjalddal Guðjónsdóttir is a certified public accountant and bookkeeper. She has worked on issues affecting people living in poverty through EAPN-Iceland (European Anti-Poverty Network in Iceland) and as a coordinator at Pepp. She was a deputy city councillor for the Socialist Party in Reykjavík.",
