  "reykjavik.A.list.5.bio": "Arna Magnea Danks is an actress and stunt coordinator, born on 31 October 1970, of Irish and Icelandic descent. She holds a BA in drama from the University of East London and has worked in theatre for decades. She is known as Iceland’s first openly trans actress and an active human rights campaigner.",
  "reykjavik.A.list.5.interests.0": "LGBTQ+ human rights",
