  "reykjavik.C.list.19.occupation": "Lawyer",
  "reykjavik.C.list.2.bio": "Róbert Ragnarsson is a public administration consultant and former municipal manager. He served as mayor of Grindavík from 2010 to 2016 and taught political science as an adjunct lecturer at the University of Iceland. He now runs the consultancy firm RR-ráðgjöf.",
  "reykjavik.C.list.2.interests.0": "Streamlining city administration",
