  "reykjavik.G.list.2.bio": "Hjördís Dröfn Vilhjálmsdóttir is a leadership and team coach with international ACC certification from ICF. She holds an MSc in management and strategy and a BSc in economics from Háskóli Íslands. She served on the board of Reginn hf. from 2013 to 2022 and has a decade of experience in change and crisis management.",
