  "reykjavik.G.list.23.occupation": "Disabled person",
  "reykjavik.G.list.3.bio": "Torfi Markússon is an operations specialist and human resources consultant who worked as HR manager at TM Software for 10 years and recruitment manager at Ráðgarður hf. for 9 years. He was previously a co-owner of the consultancy firm Intellecta ehf.",
  "reykjavik.G.list.3.interests.0": "Operational improvements",
