  "reykjavik.G.list.4.interests.1": "Creative solutions in marketing",
  "reykjavik.G.list.4.occupation": "Brand designer",
  "reykjavik.G.list.5.bio": "Jón L. Árnason is the managing director of the pension fund Lífsverk and is in 5th place on the G list (Góðan daginn) in the 2026 Reykjavík City Council elections; he became world chess champion in the under-17 category in 1977.",
  "reykjavik.G.list.5.occupation": "Managing director",
