  "reykjavik.M.list.4.bio": "Hlédís Maren Guðmundsdóttir is a sociologist, born in 1992 or 1993. She served on the board of Ung vinstri-græn from 2013 to 2015 and completed a BS degree in sociology from Háskóli Íslands. She worked as a journalist and wrote articles for Heimildin in 2020–2021, and later at Útlendingastofnun. In recent years, she has written critical opinion pieces and shifted to the right in her political views.",
