  "reykjavik.R.agenda.1.text": "Speed up development in Geldinganes with diverse housing options; increase the number of affordable housing choices.",
  "reykjavik.R.agenda.1.title": "Housing",
  "reykjavik.R.agenda.2.text": "A hiring freeze at the City where possible, with an emphasis on restraint and savings.",
  "reykjavik.R.agenda.2.title": "Hiring freeze",
  "reykjavik.R.agenda.3.text": "Push for changes to the state's monetary policy; reject agreements that involve political concessions.",
