  "vestmannaeyjar.D.list.1.bio": "Eyþór Harðarson is fleet manager at Ísfélag hf. in Vestmannaeyjar and has held that position since 2003. He is a qualified electrical engineer from Germany and has also served as chairman of Fiskmarkaður Vestmannaeyja hf. since 2009. Eyþór has been chairman of the Independence Association of Vestmannaeyjar since 2022 and received 62.6% of the vote in the party’s primary in March 2026.",
